defs.name: Value
defs.value:
pub enum Value {
    Variable(Name),
    Int(Number),
    Float(f64),
    String(String),
    Boolean(bool),
    Null,
    Enum(Name),
    List(Vec<Value>),
    Object(BTreeMap<Name, Value>),
}
